                    </div>
                    <!-- Review 2 -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                        <div class="text-accent text-2xl mb-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="font-body text-text italic mb-4">
                            "The treatment was really good, and the doctor explained everything patiently Also staffs are so friendly"
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-primary">- Daya Anandhi Jayaraman</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Review 3 -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg flex flex-col items-center text-center">
                        <div class="text-accent text-2xl mb-4">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                        </div>
                        <p class="font-body text-text italic mb-4">
                            "I chose this clinic after reading the reviews and because I was in a hurry, as my tooth was aching badly. I had considered going to Apollo, but since it was too far, I decided to c..."
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-primary">- UNNATI KISHOR</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Section -->
        <section data-section="contact" id="contact" class="bg-background py-16 md:py-24">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-4">
                    Get in Touch with Smile Dental Care
                </h2>
                <p class="font-body text-lg text-text max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
                    We're here to help you achieve and maintain a healthy, beautiful smile. Contact us today!
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
                    <!-- Contact Info -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-left border-t-4 border-primary">
                        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4 flex items-center">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-info-circle text-primary mr-3"></i> Contact Information
                        </h3>
                        <p class="font-body text-text mb-3">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-map-marker-alt text-secondary mr-2"></i>
                            Basement, Joshi & Joshi Complex, 3rd St, opp. Kailash Nagar, opp. Zudio showroom, AVM Jyothi Nagar, Sakthi Nagar, Pappakurichi Kattur, Thanjavur, Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu 620019, India
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-body text-text mb-3">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-phone text-secondary mr-2"></i>
                            Phone: <a href="tel:+919791765077" class="text-primary hover:underline">097917 65077</a>
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-body text-text mb-3">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-globe text-secondary mr-2"></i>
                            Website: <a href="http://www.smiledentalcaretrichy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">smiledentalcaretrichy.com</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Opening Hours -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg text-left border-t-4 border-secondary">
                        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4 flex items-center">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-clock text-secondary mr-3"></i> Opening Hours
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="font-body text-text space-y-2">
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Monday:</span> 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 9:00 PM</li>
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Tuesday:</span> 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 9:00 PM</li>
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Wednesday:</span> 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 9:00 PM</li>
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Thursday:</span> 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 9:00 PM</li>
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Friday:</span> 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 9:00 PM</li>
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Saturday:</span> 11:00 AM – 2:30 PM, 6:00 – 9:00 PM</li>
                            <li><span class="font-semibold">Sunday:</span> 6:00 – 8:30 PM</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Google Map -->
                    <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg border-t-4 border-accent">
                        <h3 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-4 flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot text-accent mr-3"></i> Find Us
                        </h3>
                        <div class="aspect-video w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
                            <iframe
                                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3919.789104033355!2d78.67568867494532!3d10.75168938940845!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3ba8f41e0a29f8f5%3A0x868153401c40212!2sSmile%20Dental%20Care!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1701977770000!5m2!1sen!2sin"
                                width="100%"
